These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, card-games, limeing
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, photographer, scientist, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, satire, sports, animation
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, lime, artichoke, cauliflower
1. the photographer is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person eating lime##1
3. the person watching sports movies is the designer##1
4. the person who's hobby is limeing is on the right of the photographer##1
5. the scientist is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
7. the photographer is the person eating kiwi##1
8. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
9. the person who's hobby is limeing is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | board-games  | limeing  | camping | card-games |
| Job           | photographer | designer | writer  | scientist  |
| Movie-Genre   | animation       | sports      | western | satire      |
| Food           | kiwi          | lime     | artichoke    | cauliflower     |

