.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, sprite, tea
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, kiwi, orange, papaya
4 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog, goat, pony
City: edinburgh, berlin, miami, rome
1. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the pony is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the goat##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
9. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | cola       | iced-tea | tea        |
| Food          | papaya     | kiwi       | orange   | broccoli   |
| Pet   | goat      | hedgehog       | pony     | frog    |
| City         | miami | rome | edinburgh | berlin |

