.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, electrician, librarian, security-guard
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, blueberry, artichoke, cabbage
4 different games are played: whist, domino, bridge, monopoly
 1. the person drinking tea is the person playing monopoly##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 3. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
 4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
 7. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the electrician##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the designer##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up       | tea        | mirinda        |
| Job           | electrician   | librarian | designer   | security-guard |
| Food   | grapefruit     | blueberry    | cabbage | artichoke        |
| Game           | bridge         | whist  | monopoly       | domino         |

