.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
City: hamburg, liverpool, colone, berlin
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, electronic, funk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, january, june, november
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, guinea-pig, horse
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
6. the fan of funk is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
7. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| City           | liverpool   | hamburg  | berlin | colone |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | funk       | d&b       | ambient     |
| Birthday   | june       | november    | january     | july  |
| Pet           | ferret     | guinea-pig | horse     | cat         |

