.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, social-worker, teacher, videographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, romance, spy, superhero
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, snowmobile, jet-ski, train
House: palace, tower, colonial, cottage
1. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1
2. the palace house is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the tower house is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the train is on the right of the cottage house##1
6. the cottage house is the person driving the jet-ski##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
8. the social-worker is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
9. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Job           | analyst  | teacher    | social-worker | videographer |
| Movie-Genre   | spy      | romance    | drama         | superhero    |
| Transport   | snowmobile   | motorbike     | jet-ski          | train      |
| House         | tower | palace | cottage      | colonial      |

