The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, dancer, doctor, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, scientific, thriller
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, april, november, august
 1. the tower house is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the colonial house is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the accountant is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is the colonial house##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the writer##1
 6. the tower house is on the left of the palace house##1
 7. the doctor is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the doctor is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| House          | colonial  | ranch-style | tower     | palace |
| Job           | doctor  | writer      | accountant | dancer    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific  | fantasy    | thriller  |
| Birthday           | november   | august       | january       | april      |

