.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, mirinda
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, october, december, march
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, amaryllis, daffodil, zinnia
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, scooter, taxi
 1. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the person who growsbellflower is the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | coffee | fanta     | iced-tea    | mirinda |
| Birthday       | february | december    | march | october |
| Flower         | amaryllis   | daffodil  | zinnia        | bellflower    |
| Transport   | taxi   | quad-bike | airplane    | scooter |

