6. the victorian house is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
7. the person traveling to new-york is the person driving the bus##1
8. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking 7up##1
9. the person driving the skateboard is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
