6. the person playing billiard is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
7. the person playing whist is the owner of the frog##1
8. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left##1
9. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | video-games | baking     |
