6. the fan of trance is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
7. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
8. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4     |
