3. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
5. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
7. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who likes turquise##1
9. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | tomato   | cucumber | apricot  | cranberry |
| Color   | white  | ivory   | pink   | turquise  |
| Sport           | badminton | basketball    | baseball | volleyball     |
